results.deck: Digital Eclipse Software developed remakes of classic Atari Arcade Games
results.description: Until the company's merger with ImaginEngine Corp., Digital Eclipse Software, Inc. developed conversions of classic Williams Atari titles for modern home computer systems, such as Defender, Ms.Pac-Man orÂ  Marble Madness, many of which were released in compilations. Following the merger, the company was renamed Backbone Entertainment and went on to produced original and many licensed games for various systems.
